    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You must go and slip in under the train, inside or back, some way to go through.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because all of the people traveling, you're hiding somewhere, that's all.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is the way to do this, so hiding.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I go around, day and night, I'm staying-- hanging someplace.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I came to Kharkov.",
